  <brief_title>Comparative Study of Different Neoadjuvant Therapies Before Radical Hysterectomy in Stage Ib2-IIa2 Cervical Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparative Study of Neoadjuvant Chemo/Brachytherapy and Chemotherapy Alone Before Radical Hysterectomy in Stage Ib2-IIa2 Cervical Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
